  "keyFeatures": [
    "Multiple TTS models supporting custom voice, voice design, and voice cloning",
    "Ultra-low latency streaming generation (97ms end-to-end synthesis)",
    "Support for 10 major languages with multilingual and cross-lingual capabilities",
    "Natural language instruction-based voice control and design",
    "3-second rapid voice cloning from reference audio",
    "High-fidelity speech tokenizer (12Hz/25Hz) for audio encoding and decoding"
